title: Sobble Evo Idea
body:
Bawloch

The Bawling Pokemon

Type: Water / Poison

Height: 10′9 ft      Weight: 210 lbs

Description: It lives in large lakes and can easily blend into the water. This makes the pokemon difficult to find. Some say if you out at night alone, you can hear its wailing cries in the distance.

Alt Description: This timid pokemon tail constantly drips water. It rarely fights, but it has some nasty barbs at the end of each hand that pack a poisonous surprise.

Name Inspiration: Bawling + Loch Ness Monster
